{"word":"ὑπόσπονδος","slug":"ὑπόσπονδος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n109185\" key=\"u(po/spondos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὑπόσπονδος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">σπονδή</etym>) <sense id=\"n109185.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">under a truce</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">treaty, secured by treaty,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὑπόσπονδοί τε ἔφασαν εἶναι ἕτοιμοι . . ἐκχωρὴσαι ἐκ τῆς νήσου</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:144\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.144</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὑ. ἐξέρχονται ἐκ τῆς χώρης</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:72\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.72</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:126\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">126</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κατελθεῖν ἐπὶ τὰ ἑωυτοῦ ὑ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:103\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.103</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg015.perseus-grc1:81\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><